text=Sometimes at night during goodnight circle we would sing this song.  It's always sad, but it's even sadder when we sing it on the last few nights of camp.   Sometimes on these days I thought I should be crying but I wouldn't be, so I would think about this song.\\\%0a%0a%0a%0a%25center%25[[Fritz|M]]
